{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_05_03",
  "title": "サニーピース 05 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見まつりの翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― The day after the Hoshimi Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "それでね、お父さんが新しい浴衣を買ってくれて\nお母さんが着付けしてくれたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ listen‚ Dad bought me a new yukata\nand Mom helped me put it on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りの会場に行ったら、人がいーっぱいいて\nいろんな屋台が出てて、わたあめとか金魚すくい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were sooooo many people at the festival‚\nand there were all these stalls like cotton candy and goldfish scooping…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.2773699563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　魚魚っとさんのかき氷を食べたんだよ\n冷たくて美味しかったなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's right! I ate some Toto-san shaved ice\nit was so cold and delicious",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1973699372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらちゃんって魚魚っとさんが大好きだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really love Toto-san‚ Sakura",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1973699372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私には良さがよく分からないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't really get the appeal‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あのぎょろっとしたつぶらな瞳がいいんだよ～\n……でも、途中で雨が沢山降ってきて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those round‚ sparkly eyes are the best part!\n…But then it started raining really hard‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "流星群を見るのは無理かなって諦めかけたんだけど……\nその時、奇跡が起こったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I almost gave up on seeing the meteor shower…\nBut then‚ a miracle happened!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "急に雨が止んで、雲が晴れて星空が見えたんだよ！\nおかげで流星群を見ることが出来たんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suddenly the rain stopped‚ the clouds cleared‚ and the starry sky appeared!\nThanks to that‚ I was able to see the meteor shower",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.7277999995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "凄い！　奇跡ってあるんだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing! So miracles really do happen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7277999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらちゃんは流れ星にどんなお願いをしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did you wish for on the shooting stars‚ Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.2711335616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、「来年は友ちゃんと一緒にお祭りに\n来られますように」ってお願いしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I wished \"I hope I can come to the festival\nwith Tomo next year.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだね、来年は絶対に一緒に行こう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ let's definitely go together next year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0714506901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.5729328357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、そうだ！　実はやりたいことがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's right! Actually‚ there's something I want to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5729328357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この間映画で観たんだけど、ウィッシュリストや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw it in a movie recently—they're called wish lists",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5856685118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バケットリストって呼ばれているものがあるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "or bucket lists.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.125668283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "日本語だと『やってみたかったリスト』になるのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In our language‚ I guess it's like a \"Things I Wanted to Try List\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.125668283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「死ぬまでにやりたいこと」を書き残すの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You write down all the \"things you want to do before you die.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それをすると自分の中にあるやりたいことが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say it makes what you want to do clearer‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8188661692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "明確になって、夢が実現しやすくなるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and makes your dreams easier to achieve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.216802259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～、面白そう！　私達もそのリストを作ろうよ\nもちろん一番最初に書くお願いは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa~ That sounds fun! Let's make a list too\nOf course‚ the very first wish to write is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.6478230911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「二人で一緒に星見まつりに行く」だよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Going to the Hoshimi Festival together‚\" right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6478230911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3747790772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "その日から私達は、やりたいと思ったことを\nノートに書き込むようになったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From that day on‚ we started writing down\neverything we wanted to do in a notebook",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それが、さくらちゃんの\n『やってみたかったリスト』の始まりなのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that was the beginning\nof your \"Things I Wanted to Try List‚\" Sakura-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "友ちゃんといるとやりたいことが次々思いついて\nノートは凄い速さで埋まっていったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was with Tomo‚ ideas just kept coming one after another‚\nand the notebook filled up so fast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "リストが増え過ぎて「全部やり終わる頃には二人とも\nおばあちゃんになってるね」って笑ったりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'd laugh and say‚ \"By the time we finish all of these‚\nwe'll both be grandmas.\" …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、一年が経って、星見まつりが近づく頃には\n友ちゃんの病状はかなり悪化して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But a year passed‚ and as the Hoshimi Festival drew near‚\nTomo's condition took a turn for the worse…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2666570028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.6464118757
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.6464118757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらちゃん、この間はごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ sorry about the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6964118757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "せっかくお見舞いに来てくれたのに会えなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You came all the way to visit me‚ but I couldn't see you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2999903362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "具合が悪かったんだから仕方ないよ\nでも今日は顔色がいいみたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ you weren't feeling well.\nBut you look like you have more color in your face today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.0952731781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.3949665505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん、もうすぐライブを観に東京に行くから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm going to Tokyo soon to see a concert‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3949665505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "友ちゃん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Tomo",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "体も気合いが入ってるのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so maybe my body's just getting pumped up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.6666407269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
